ossible.                                                        5. I really appreciate all the kind words and thoughts previously! Thank you everyone for your good vibes. If you have any more to spare this week please keep sending them! Hopefully no further treatment needed!                  #forbiddenfruit #donteatit #mango #tumor #cancer #fuckcancer</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/PKlaeme</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[WorksInHotelDoesntTravel]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>My 13 year old just discovered Freddie Mercury on YouTube.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/hBuC6ep</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qGQoMp1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Needless to say she was a little impressed.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/hBuC6ep</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MayMyEnemiesLiveLong]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>In other news, society continues to spiral down the drain.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/kHEPDQ4</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/i2Li2cz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>These things are inevitable I guess, but it’s still scary to watch.

